like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"cce09de60e9b2cf31c24f734f67992ad16bbdd5e","tid":1032645,"uid":41245,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:51:00.000Z","msg":"俾英國知道可以公投唔認數就唔洗搞大頭佛啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T17:52:37.000Z","msg":"你睇清新上年台灣公投結果係點先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/2018年中華民國全國性公民投票\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2018%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E6%80%A7%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLRBk8ry%2Bv12G5j1RUyKX8i0%3D&h=45384875\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/2018年中華民國全國性公民投票</a><br />\n首先：公投通過「民法婚姻」限定一男一女（公投10），否決「民法婚姻」包含同性結婚（公投14）<br />\n<br />\n然後：公投通過「另立專法」保障同性關係，而不修改「民法婚姻」定義（公投12）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家呢條草案咪就係執行緊公投結果囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef71ab098bb3f1b558aae83759a4bec7ec4636e2","tid":1032645,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410e4a9a76a13e7ee5d7efb255445863d5f49782","tid":1032645,"uid":13100,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:25:05.000Z","msg":"我睇報導，台灣有班同性戀係「反專法、入民法」<br />\n因為佢地覺得另《同性婚姻法》、《同性關係法》之類，就算內容文字同一男一女結緍嘅《民法婚姻》一模一樣都好，都係岐視<br />\n佢地認為，大家都係台灣人，點解佢地唔可以用《民法婚姻》嚟結婚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋依家呢條草案嘅名唔係《同性婚姻法》，係《司法院釋字第748號解釋施行法》<br />\n「釋字748號」係司法院法官團2017年解釋憲法，認為應保障同性關係權利<br />\n因為政府唔想刺激反同團體，所以另立同性專法都唔敢喺個法律標題加「同性婚姻」幾隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家係睇，嗰班要用《民法婚姻》嚟同性結婚，唔要立專法嘅死硬派肯唔肯袋住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以及反同團體遊唔遊說到將依家草案內文中「同性婚姻」改成「同性結合」「同性共同生活」之類，刪去「婚姻」兩隻字喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7391e098589a11a9ac3b01ff122162a842632a","tid":1032645,"uid":238370,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f8b65fb866a7d30a491c255322f1a15840135f00","tid":1032645,"uid":24160,"like":22,"dislike":9,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:57:33.000Z","msg":"希望可以實行得到啦<br />\n想有朝一日見到香港同婚合法化<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:00:54.000Z","msg":"香港好撚難啦，垃圾會有老鼠芬何軍妖之流，連性傾向歧視同伴侶法都係到啊吱啊咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ffc7bbdac9ffb5d49d1a666d207fa04758bfca","tid":1032645,"uid":161232,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:01:59.000Z","msg":"文明社會進步"},{"pid":"17127de0cbe7a05a36d4b6ada24a40ce0fecfc4e","tid":1032645,"uid":57677,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"bc7391e098589a11a9ac3b01ff122162a842632a","tid":1032645,"uid":238370,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f8b65fb866a7d30a491c255322f1a15840135f00","tid":1032645,"uid":24160,"like":22,"dislike":9,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:57:33.000Z","msg":"希望可以實行得到啦<br />\n想有朝一日見到香港同婚合法化<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" 